sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Caller
  participant S as auditService
  participant P as Provider (append-only)
  participant EV as EventPublisher port

  Note over C,S: record(spec) — serialized per namespace
  C->>S: record({ action, actor, correlationId, ... })
  S->>P: tail(namespace)
  P-->>S: previous record (or null)
  S->>S: sequence = prev.sequence + 1<br/>prevChecksum = prev.checksum (or GENESIS)<br/>checksum = sha256(content + prevChecksum) → freeze
  S->>P: append(namespace, record)  (immutable)
  S->>EV: AuditRecorded (summary)
  S-->>C: frozen record

  Note over C,S: verify(namespace) — integrity
  C->>S: verify()
  S->>P: scan(namespace)
  P-->>S: records (append order)
  loop each record i
    S->>S: checksum matches content?  prevChecksum == records[i-1].checksum?  sequence == i?
  end
  alt intact
    S->>EV: AuditVerified
    S-->>C: { ok: true, checked }
  else tampered / broken / gap
    S->>EV: AuditIntegrityFailure
    S-->>C: { ok: false, issues }
  end
